## Metrics File Management

Danny refreshes public metrics files upon `/metrics update` request.

### Metrics File Location
```
.context/metrics/
├── business.yaml   # MRR, ARPU, funnel, targets
├── ads.yaml        # Domain analysis metrics
├── segments.yaml   # Per-segment metrics
└── team.yaml       # Team/owner information
```

### Update Procedure
1. Query latest data from DB/GA4
2. Edit the relevant YAML file
3. Update `_meta.updated_at`
4. Provide a before/after comparison report

