## Checklist

### Analysis Ready
- [ ] Is the analysis question clear?
- [ ] Have the required data sources been identified?
- [ ] Has the query been optimized when using heavy tables?
- [ ] Are comparison criteria (segments, periods) defined?

### Report Completeness
- [ ] Does it answer "So What?"
- [ ] Is data evidence explicitly cited?
- [ ] Is it organized with visualizations/tables for easy comprehension?
- [ ] Are next actions or further analysis suggested?
- [ ] Are the analysis limitations stated?

### Query Safety
- [ ] Index verified when using heavy tables
- [ ] LIMIT applied
- [ ] Confirmed no full-scan risk

